(4, 'HIM', '4cc51547-88ae-49a2-bf7e-0ef65ee7a94c', 'His Infernal Majesty;HER', 'Helsinki[39d62198-1e76-4de4-b079-e86e3a393bbc]', '100116[6a264f94-6ff1-30b1-9a81-41f7bfabd616]', '1991;1995', '1993;2017-12-31', '99;7;62;98;Lovex_not_found;124;The Vantages_not_found', '200015;200010', '2000025;2000574;2000575;2001137', '5', '[AllMusic (6)‚Ė†https://www.allmusic.com/artist/mn0000577091];[MusicBrainz (6)‚Ė†https://musicbrainz.org/artist/4cc51547-88ae-49a2-bf7e-0ef65ee7a94c];[Discogs (6)‚Ė†https://www.discogs.com/artist/95251];[Spotify (3)‚Ė†https://open.spotify.com/artist/74aLweE8FHHf4yN5TWv1GM];[Deezer (3)‚Ė†https://www.deezer.com/artist/1071];[IMDb (6)‚Ė†https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1367079/];[Last.fm (6)‚Ė†https://www.last.fm/music/Him];[Muzikum (7)‚Ė†http://muzikum.eu/en/122-9893/him/lyrics.html];[MySpace (2)‚Ė†https://myspace.com/heartagram];[Official Website (2)‚Ė†http://www.heartagram.com/];[Saintscream (6)‚Ė†https://www.saintscream.ru/];[Library of Congress (6)‚Ė†http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/no2005028429];[Instagram (2)‚Ė†https://www.instagram.com/heartagram/];[Rate Your Music (6)‚Ė†https://rateyourmusic.com/artist/him];[WorldCat (6)‚Ė†https://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-no2005028429];[Apple Music (4)‚Ė†https://itunes.apple.com/artist/id416746260];[Secondhandsongs (6)‚Ė†https://secondhandsongs.com/artist/557];[X (2)‚Ė†https://twitter.com/theheartagram];[Facebook (2)‚Ė†https://www.facebook.com/theheartagram];[Songkick (6)‚Ė†https://www.songkick.com/artists/338751];[Tidal (3)‚Ė†https://tidal.com/artist/3051];[VIAF (6)‚Ė†http://viaf.org/viaf/146522260];[Wikidata (6)‚Ė†https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q23479];[YouTube (3)‚Ė†https://www.youtube.com/user/him];[Wikipedia (6)‚Ė†https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HIM_(Finnish_band)];[Sporcle (6)‚Ė†https://www.sporcle.com/playlists/mediabinger/him];[Setlist.fm (6)‚Ė†https://www.setlist.fm/setlists/him-4bd6cf0a.html];[AZ (7)‚Ė†https://www.azlyrics.com/h/him.html];[Genius (7)‚Ė†https://genius.com/artists/Him];[Amazon Music (4)‚Ė†https://www.amazon.com/music/player/artists/B000QJO5W4/him];[RuTracker (5)‚Ė†https://rutracker.org/forum/tracker.php?nm=HIM%20discography];[Musixmatch (7)‚Ė†https://www.musixmatch.com/artist/HiM];[YouTube Music (3)‚Ė†https://music.youtube.com/channel/UCihm_iUlNxA9Si_1z08KZyQ];[Official Store (4)‚Ė†https://eu.heartagram.com/];[The Pirate Bay (5)‚Ė†https://thepiratebay.org/search.php?q=him&audio=on];[Reddit (2)‚Ė†https://www.reddit.com/r/HIM/]', 'HIM (sometimes stylized as H.I.M.) was a Finnish gothic rock band from Helsinki. First formed in 1991 by vocalist Ville Valo and bassist Mikko \"Mige\" Paananen under the name His Infernal Majesty‚Ė† the band broke up after only a few years‚Ė† only to be reformed in 1995 by Valo and guitarist Mikko \"Linde\" Lindstr√∂m. After being rejoined by Mige‚Ė† as well as keyboardist Antto Melasniemi and drummer Juhana \"P√§tk√§\" Rantala‚Ė† the band‚Ė† now called HIM‚Ė† released its debut album Greatest Lovesongs Vol. 666 in 1997. In 2000‚Ė† now with drummer Mika \"Gas Lipstick\" Karppinen and keyboardist Juska Salminen‚Ė† the band released Razorblade Romance‚Ė† which reached the number one spot in Finland‚Ė† Austria and Germany. The first single \"Join Me in Death\" also charted at number one in Finland and Germany‚Ė† eventually going platinum and gold‚Ė† respectively. Following the addition of Janne \"Burton\" Puurtinen on keyboards‚Ė† HIM released Deep Shadows and Brilliant Highlights (2001) and Love Metal (2003). Both cracked the top ten in several countries and allowed the band to tour in the United Kingdom and the United States for the first time.\nIn 2005‚Ė† HIM released Dark Light‚Ė† which became the group‚Ėąs most commercially successful album to date. HIM also became the first Finnish group in history to receive a gold record in the US. In 2007‚Ė† HIM released Venus Doom‚Ė† the making of which was marred by problems in Valo‚Ėąs personal life. Nevertheless‚Ė† the album gave the band its highest chart position in the US at number twelve. After 2010‚Ėąs Screamworks: Love in Theory and Practice‚Ė† HIM went on a hiatus after Gas Lipstick was forced to take medical leave. Following several months of uncertainty‚Ė† the band regrouped and released the album Tears on Tape in 2013. Gas Lipstick announced his departure from the band in 2015 and was subsequently replaced by Jukka \"Kosmo\" Kr√∂ger. On 5 March 2017‚Ė† HIM announced that the band would be disbanding following a farewell tour in 2017. The band played its final show on New Year‚Ėąs Eve 2017 as a part of its annual Helldone Festival.\nHIM is one of the most commercially successful Finnish bands of all time‚Ė† with sales of over ten million records. HIM has also received numerous accolades‚Ė† including eight Emma Awards. The band is known for its distinct sound‚Ė† which combines more melodic and melancholic elements with heavier influences. This made it difficult for audiences to categorize HIM‚Ėąs music‚Ė† which led to the band coining the term \"love metal\". HIM is also known for its logo‚Ė† the heartagram‚Ė† which has made numerous appearances in other media.', 'http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/H/HIM/Audio/Albums/1997.11.03. Greatest Lovesongs Vol. 666/1997.11.03. Standard Edition/03. Wicked Game [Chris Isaak cover].mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/H/HIM/Audio/Albums/2000.01.24. Razorblade Romance/2000.01.24. Standard Edition/04. Right Here in My Arms.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/H/HIM/Audio/Albums/2000.01.24. Razorblade Romance/2000.01.24. Standard Edition/03. Join Me in Death.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/H/HIM/Audio/Albums/2005.09.23. Dark Light/2005.09.23. Standard Edition/02. Rip Out the Wings of a Butterfly.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/H/HIM/Audio/Albums/2003.04.11. Love Metal/2003.04.11. Standard Edition/02. The Funeral of Hearts.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/H/HIM/Audio/Albums/2000.01.24. Razorblade Romance/2000.01.24. Standard Edition/05. Gone with the Sin.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/H/HIM/Audio/Albums/2005.09.23. Dark Light/2005.09.23. Standard Edition/04. Killing Loneliness.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/H/HIM/Audio/Albums/2000.01.24. Razorblade Romance/2000.01.24. Standard Edition/02. Poison Girl.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/H/HIM/Audio/Albums/2003.04.11. Love Metal/2003.04.11. Standard Edition/06. The Sacrament.mp3', 'Wicked Game‚Ė†Right Here in My Arms‚Ė†Join Me In Death‚Ė†Wings of a Butterfly‚Ė†The Funeral of Hearts‚Ė†Gone With The Sin‚Ė†Killing Loneliness‚Ė†Poison Girl‚Ė†The Sacrament‚Ė†Join Me‚Ė†Buried Alive by Love‚Ė†In Joy And Sorrow‚Ė†Vampire Heart‚Ė†Heartache Every Moment‚Ė†When Love and Death Embrace‚Ė†Pretending‚Ė†Your Sweet 666‚Ė†Razorblade Kiss‚Ė†Close to the Flame‚Ė†Heaven Tonight‚Ė†Join Me - Razorblade Mix‚Ė†Under the Rose‚Ė†Death is In Love With Us‚Ė†Resurrection‚Ė†Soul on Fire‚Ė†Your Sweet Six Six Six‚Ė†For You‚Ė†Bury Me Deep Inside Your Heart‚Ė†Rip Out the Wings of a Butterfly‚Ė†Passion%36s Killing Floor‚Ė†And Love Said No‚Ė†Heartkiller‚Ė†Behind The Crimson Door‚Ė†Solitary Man‚Ė†Venus Doom‚Ė†Sweet Pandemonium‚Ė†Dark Light‚Ė†Beautiful‚Ė†The Heartless‚Ė†Lose You Tonight‚Ė†Beyond Redemption‚Ė†Drunk on Shadows‚Ė†The Kiss Of Dawn‚Ė†One Last Time‚Ė†Circle of Fear‚Ė†The Face of God‚Ė†Endless Dark‚Ė†Play Dead‚Ė†Our Diabolikal Rapture‚Ė†Salt in Our Wounds‚Ė†Bleed Well‚Ė†The Beginning Of The End‚Ė†The Path‚Ė†It%36s All Tears (Drown In This Love)‚Ė†Please Don%36t Let It Go‚Ė†This Fortress of Tears‚Ė†Sleepwalking Past Hope‚Ė†In The NightSide Of Eden‚Ė†Love In Cold Blood‚Ė†I love you‚Ė†Scared To Death‚Ė†Love You Like I Do‚Ė†Join Me In Death - Strongroom Mix‚Ė†Sigillum Diaboli‚Ė†Don%36t Close Your Heart‚Ė†I Love You (Prelude To Tragedy)‚Ė†Song Or Suicide‚Ė†In Venere Veritas‚Ė†Cyanide Sun‚Ė†(Don%36t Fear) The Reaper‚Ė†Dying Song‚Ė†Katherine Wheel‚Ė†You Are the One‚Ė†Love, The Hardest Way‚Ė†In The Arms Of Rain‚Ė†Dead Lovers%36 Lane‚Ė†Don%36t Fear the Reaper‚Ė†Ode To Solitude‚Ė†Like St. Valentine‚Ė†Shatter Me With Hope‚Ė†All Lips Go Blue‚Ė†Bury Me Deep