bands around the city. In 1991‚Ė† he co-founded and became the lead singer and main songwriter of HIM‚Ė† which would go on to become one of the most successful Finnish bands of all time and the first to receive a gold record in the United States. Outside of HIM‚Ė† Valo has collaborated with various other bands and artists during his career‚Ė† including Agents‚Ė† The 69 Eyes‚Ė† and Apocalyptica. In 2020‚Ė† Valo embarked on a solo career under the moniker VV. His debut album Neon Noir was released in 2023.\nHe is also the creator of the heartagram‚Ė† HIM‚Ėąs trademarked symbol‚Ė† which has achieved great popularity outside of the band‚Ėąs fanbase. Valo has received several accolades in the music industry and has been regarded as a sex symbol by several publications.', 'http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/02. Run Away from the Sun.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/01. Echolocate Your Love.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/05. The Foreverlost.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/07. Salute the Sanguine.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/10. Saturnine Saturnalia.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/04. Loveletting.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/06. Baby Lacrimarium.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/09. Heartful of Ghosts.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/08. In Trenodia.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/V/VV/Audio/Albums/2023.01.13. Neon Noir/2023.01.13. Standard Edition/11. Zener 