(120, 'Various Artists', '89ad4ac3-39f7-470e-963a-56509c546377', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '[discogs‚Ė†https://www.discogs.com/artist/194];[free streaming‚Ė†https://open.spotify.com/artist/0LyfQWJT6nXafLPZqxe9Of];[last.fm‚Ė†https://www.last.fm/music/Various+Artists];[streaming‚Ė†https://music.amazon.com/artists/B000QJO93Y];[wikidata‚Ė†https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q3108914]', 'Various Artists is a curated collection that celebrates musical diversity‚ÄĒbringing together standout singles and hidden gems from a wide range of artists. From genre-defying collaborations to rare releases that never made it onto main records, this playlist is a sonic mosaic of voices, styles, and eras. Whether you\'re discovering new favorites or revisiting timeless tracks, each song stands on its own while contributing to a rich, collective soundscape.', NULL, 'Cranberries - Animal Instinct‚Ė†What A Wonderful World‚Ė†Jingle Bell Rock‚Ė†Let%36s Stay Together‚Ė†The Reason‚Ė†Smoke Signals‚Ė†Fools‚Ė†Bleeders‚Ė†Intro‚Ė†James Brown - I Got You (I Feel Good)‚Ė†Mr. Brightside‚Ė†The Great Escape‚Ė†I Want You Back‚Ė†I Miss You‚Ė†Viva Della Rocca‚Ė†Love Is All Around‚Ė†Really And Truly‚Ė†At Last‚Ė†Give Me A Reason‚Ė†Kryptonite‚Ė†Metropolitan Jazz Affair / Escapism‚Ė†The Quantic Soul Orchestra Feat Alice Russel / Feeling Good‚Ė†Paolo Fedreghini & Marco Bianchi / Oriental Smile‚Ė†Tom Waits, Peter Murphy - Christmas Sucks‚Ė†Shiver‚Ė†Jamie Cullum / It Ain%36t Necessarely So‚Ė†Take Me Back‚Ė†Roxy Music - More than this‚Ė†Friday I%36m In Love‚Ė†Nick Cave,Anita Lane - Bedazzled‚Ė†Hello‚Ė†Sicania Soul Feat Lara Luppi / Life Is A Tree (Live - Take 2)‚Ė†Beady Belle Feat Beat S.Lech / Goldilocks‚Ė†Povo / Uam Uam‚Ė†Micha√ęl Buble / Peroxide Swing‚Ė†Nick Holder / Sometime I%36m Blue‚Ė†Nick Cave, PJ Harvey - Henry Lee‚Ė†Tosca / Pyjama‚Ė†Wind Of Change‚Ė†Kylie Eastwood / Big Noise (From Winnetka)‚Ė†Kinny & Horn / Sacred Life‚Ė†Lonesome Town‚Ė†Muriel Zoe / Bye Bye Blackbird‚Ė†Rhythm Factor