unit Walk√ľre and has maintained a successful solo career since 2017 under the FlyingDog label. Yasuno was born in Kyoto but raised in Wakuya, Miyagi Prefecture. Her interest in anime began in childhood after watching series like Sailor Moon and Magic Knight Rayearth. During high school, she used her own savings to enroll in the Avex Artist Academy\'s voice acting course. Yasuno made her professional debut in 2009. Her first lead role came in 2011 as Kizuna Todoroki in the film Kizuna Ichigeki. Her career saw a significant rise in 2015 when she was cast as the main heroine, Megumi KatŇć, in Saekano. Her voice is noted for its versatility, ranging from quiet, deadpan characters to energetic heroes and mature women.', 'http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kiyono Yasuno/Audio/Albums/2018.11.07. Egao/07. ROCKET BEAT.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kiyono Yasuno/Audio/Albums/2018.11.07. Egao/04. Wonder Shot.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kiyono Yasuno/Audio/Albums/2018.11.07. Egao/01. Bokuno Venus.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kiyono Yasuno/Audio/Singles/2018.11.07. Egao/2018.04.25. ROCKET BEAT/02. Aitakute.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kiyono Yasuno/Audio/Albums/2018.11.07. Egao/02. Fuwafuwato Shiteru.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kiyono Yasuno/Audio/Albums/2018.11.07. Egao/03. Egao.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kiyono Yasuno/Audio/Albums/2018.11.07. Egao/06. Nagekino Sora.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kiyono Yasuno/Audio/Albums/2018.11.07. Egao/05. Kasukana Kanashimi.mp3', '„É≠„āĪ„ÉÉ„Éą„Éď„Éľ„Éą‚Ė†Onnaji Kimochi.‚Ė†„Ā°„ĀĄ„Āē„Ā™„Ā≤„Ā®„Ā§„Ā∂‚Ė†A piece of cake‚Ė†echoes‚Ė†„É≠„āĪ„ÉÉ„Éą„Éď„Éľ„Éą -TV„āĶ„ā§„āļ-‚Ė†Felicita‚Ė†śôī„āĆś®°śßė‚Ė†ÁĒü„Āć„āč‚Ė†„āĘ„Éę„āī„É™„āļ„É†‚Ė†Hare Moyo‚Ė†Fallen‚Ė†„Āä„Āč„Āą„āä„Äā‚Ė†Rocket Beat‚Ė†Uchu no Hosoku‚Ė†śúąŚ§ú„Āę„Éě„Éľ„É°„ā§„ÉČ‚Ė†ťÄĘ„ĀĄ„Āü„ĀŹ„Ā¶‚Ė†Chiisana Hitotsubu‚Ė†kiss! kiss! kiss!‚Ė†śĀč„Āô„āčÁßĀ„āę„É©„Éľ‚Ė†śįīťöõFOREVER‚Ė†Seiki no Shukusai‚Ė†I remember‚Ė†„Āľ„ĀŹ„Āģ„Éī„ā£„Éľ„Éä„āĻ‚Ė†DestinoÔĹěśĀč„ĀĮšłÄÁßí„Āģśįłť