zer.com/artist/4897020];[Official Store (4)‚Ė†https://shop.hirose-kohmi.com/];[Genius (7)‚Ė†https://genius.com/artists/Kohmi-hirose]', 'Kohmi Hirose (ŚļÉÁÄ¨ ť¶ôÁĺé, Hirose KŇćmi, born April 12, 1966) is a Japanese pop singer, songwriter, and composer. Known for her powerful vocal range and high-energy performances, she became one of the most successful J-pop artists of the 1990s. She is widely referred to by the Japanese public as the \"Winter Queen\" (Fuyu no JoŇć) due to her long-standing association with the winter sporting goods company Alpen, which used her music in its annual advertising campaigns for decades.\nBorn in Nachikatsuura, Wakayama and raised in Fukuoka, Hirose was a musical prodigy who began piano at age four and was composing by age five. She attended the Kunitachi College of Music, specializing in composition. During her university years, she traveled to Los Angeles to study pop music, where she trained under Seth Riggs, the renowned vocal coach for stars like Michael Jackson and Whitney Houston.', 'http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kohmi Hirose/Audio/Compilations/1998.11.11. The Best Love Winters/03. „É≠„Éě„É≥„āĻ„ĀģÁ•ěśßė.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kohmi Hirose/Audio/Compilations/1998.11.11. The Best Love Winters/08. promise.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kohmi Hirose/Audio/Compilations/1998.11.11. The Best Love Winters/10. Groovy!.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kohmi Hirose/Audio/Compilations/1998.11.11. The Best Love Winters/05. „ā≤„É¨„É≥„Éá„ĀĆ„Ā®„ĀĎ„āč„ĀĽ„Ā©śĀč„Āó„Āü„ĀĄ.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kohmi Hirose/Audio/Compilations/1998.11.11. The Best Love Winters/04. ŚĻł„Āõ„āí„Ā§„Āč„ĀŅ„Āü„ĀĄ.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kohmi Hirose/Audio/Compilations/1998.11.11. The Best Love Winters/07. ÁúüŚÜ¨„ĀģŚłį„āäťĀď.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kohmi Hirose/Audio/Compilations/1998.11.11. The Best Love Winters/01. śĄõ„ĀĆ„Āā„āĆ„ĀįŚ§ßšłąŚ§ę.mp3^http://127.0.0.1:8887//Music/K/Kohmi Hirose/Audio/Compilations/1998.11.11. The B