(65, 'Pretending', NULL, '4', '2001.07.02.', 'BMG', 'Gothic Rock', '\"Pretending\" is a song by the Finnish band HIM, released in 2001 as the fifth track from their album Deep Shadows and Brilliant Highlights. It sold 7,641 copies in Finland.\n\nIn 2006, an acoustic version of \"Pretending\" was released as a double-A-side single along with the string version of \"In Joy and Sorrow\" on the album Uneasy Listening Vol. 1. The orchestral \"In Joy and Sorrow\" is the fifth track on the compilation, while the acoustic \"Pretending\" was an exclusive sixteenth track only available by buying the album from Best Buy. \"In Joy and Sorrow\"/\"Pretending\" reached No. 1 in Finland.\n\nThe first track on the international release is a shorter version than the official album version. The original version is 3:55 while the single version is 3:44.', 'Bass‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄDouble Bass~Lead Vocals‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄGuitar~Guitar~Drums~Keyboard‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄPiano', NULL, '470', '21‚Ė†22‚Ė†23‚Ė†27‚Ė†28', 'b379fe62-d98b-4969-9191-251a3b46dda8', '~Pretending~[{22}]‚Ė†~Please Don‚ĖÄt Let It Go~[{22}]‚Ė†~Lose You Tonight~[{22}]', NULL, NULL),
(66, 'In Joy and Sorrow', NULL, '4', '2001.09.12.', 'BMG', 'Alternative Rock', 'In Joy and Sorrow is a single by HIM which came out on September 12, 2001, taken from their album Deep Shadows and Brilliant Highlights released in 2001.', 'Bass‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄDouble Bass~Lead Vocals‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄGuitar~Guitar~Drums~Keyboard‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄPiano', NULL, '474;470', '21‚Ė†22‚Ė†23‚Ė†27‚Ė†28', '655326e9-fc33-4ac9-805c-23067d4bba22', '~In Joy and Sorrow~[{22}]‚Ė†~Salt in Our Wounds~[{22}]‚Ė†~Beautiful~[{22}]‚Ė†~Again~[{22}]', NULL, NULL),
(67, 'Close to the Flame', NULL, '4', '2002.01.14.', 'BMG', 'Alternative Rock', 'Close to the Flame is a single by HIM which came out on January 14, 2002, taken from their album Deep Shadows and Brilliant Highlights released in 2001.', 'Bass‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄDouble Bass~Lead Vocals‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄGuitar~Guitar~Drums~Keyboard‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄPiano', NULL, '4_bnd', '21‚Ė†22‚Ė†23‚Ė†27‚Ė†28', '0fbb35f8-61c7-4a26-b91e-b2ad1876c5a8', '~Heartache Every Moment~[{22}]‚Ė†~Close to the Flame~[{22}]‚Ė†~Salt in Our Wounds~[{22}]‚Ė†~In Joy and Sorrow~[{22}]‚Ė†~Pretending~[{22}]', NULL, NULL),
