(71, 'The Sacrament', NULL, '4', '2003.06.27.', 'BMG', 'Gothic Rock', 'The Sacrament is a song by the Finnish band HIM, released in 2003. It is the sixth track and third single from the album Love Metal. The music video was directed by Bam Margera. The song was used over the end credits of the 2007 Japanese anime, Highlander: The Search for Vengeance.', 'Bass‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄDouble Bass~Lead Vocals‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄGuitar~Guitar~Drums~Keyboard‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄPiano', NULL, '474;447', '21‚Ė†22‚Ė†23‚Ė†27‚Ė†28', '5b129c17-b49f-4a6d-bdea-30104d255f49', '~The Sacrament~[{22}]‚Ė†~Buried Alive by Love~[{22}]‚Ė†~Buried Alive By Love~[{22}]', NULL, NULL),
(72, 'Solitary Man', NULL, '4', '2004.03.01.', 'BMG', 'Alternative Rock;Pop Rock', 'Solitary Man is a song written by American musician Neil Diamond, who recorded the song for Bang Records in late January 1966. It has since been covered many times, notably by T. G. Sheppard, Gianni Morandi, Chris Isaak, Johnny Cash and HIM.', 'Bass‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄDouble Bass~Lead Vocals‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄGuitar~Guitar~Drums~Keyboard‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄPiano', NULL, '471', '21‚Ė†22‚Ė†23‚Ė†27‚Ė†28', '294c99b4-ab95-466e-a45c-a52488126e24', '~Please Don‚ĖÄt Let It Go~[{22}]‚Ė†~Join Me in Death~[{22}]‚Ė†~Your Sweet Six Six Six~[{22}]‚Ė†~Solitary Man~[{Neil Diamond_not_found}]‚Ė†~Right Here in My Arms~[{22}]', NULL, NULL),
