(138, 'Neon Noir', NULL, '62', '2023.01.13.', 'Heartagram Records', 'Gothic Rock', 'Neon Noir is the debut solo studio album by Finnish singer-songwriter Ville Valo, released on January 13, 2023, under the moniker VV through Heartagram Records and distributed by Spinefarm. It marks Valo\'s first full-length musical project since the 2017 disbandment of the gothic rock band HIM, for which he was the lead vocalist and primary songwriter. Written, recorded, and produced entirely by Valo during the COVID-19 pandemic, the album was a solo endeavor in the truest sense; he performed all instruments and handled the engineering in his home studio. Valo described the process as a \"survival kit\" during the global lockdowns, bridge-building between his past work with HIM and his future as a solo artist.\nThe album\'s sound is a continuation of the \"Love Metal\" genre pioneered by HIM, blending elements of Gothic Rock: Melancholy atmospheres and deep, melodic vocals, Alternative Rock: 80s-inspired synthesizers and driving guitar riffs and New Wave: Influences from bands like The Cure and Depeche Mode. Thematically, Neon Noir explores the juxtaposition of light and darkness, reflected in its title. Valo has characterized the lyrical content as \"the sound of a moth to a flame,\" focusing on themes of romance, mortality, and nocturnal longing. The album was preceded by several singles, including \"Loveletting,\" \"Echolocate Your Love,\" and \"The Foreverlost.\" Upon its release, Neon Noir debuted at number one on the Finnish Albums Chart and received positive reviews from critics, who praised Valo‚Äôs ability to evolve his signature sound while maintaining the emotional core that defined his earlier career.', 'Lead Vocals‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄBass‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄDrums‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄGuitar', NULL, '471;22', '22', '', 'data-writer‚Ė†~Baby Lacrimarium~[{22}]‚Ė†~Saturnine Saturnalia~[{22}]‚Ė†~Echolocate Your Love~[{22}]‚Ė†~Run Away from the Sun~[{22}]‚Ė†~Loveletting~[{22}]‚Ė†~Vertigo Eyes~[{22}]‚Ė†~Neon Noir~[{22}]‚Ė†~In Trenodia~[{22}]‚Ė†~Zener Solitaire~[{22}]‚Ė†~Salute the Sanguine~[{22}]‚Ė†~The Foreverlost~[{22}]', NULL, NULL),
