(187, 'Poison Arrow', NULL, '4', '2005.11.05.', 'Sire', 'Alternative Rock;Gothic Metal;Gothic Rock;Pop Rock', 'HIM: Poison Arrow reveals for the first time the full story of Finlands finest, with rare footage, exclusive band interviews and footage, location shoots, previously unpublished photographs and a host of other features. It features rare HIM footage featured throughout the film as well as exclusive interviews with the band and those who know them best, including: singer Villes father, Kari Valo - close friend and professional colleague of the band, Silke Yli-Sirnioe - HIM\'s PR and Tour Organiser, Tomi Saarinen - Top Finnish DJ from YLEX, the country\'s premier rock station, Steve Price - founder of Goth Metal Meltdown magazine, Natasha Scharf - and many, many more.', 'Bass‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄDouble Bass~Lead Vocals‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄGuitar~Guitar~Drums~Keyboard‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄPiano', NULL, '447', '21‚Ė†22‚Ė†23‚Ė†27‚Ė†28', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
