(202, 'Summer Wine', NULL, '62', '2007.01.26.', 'Self-released record', 'Gothic Rock;Rock', 'Summer Wine is a song written by Lee Hazlewood. Hazlewood originally performed it with Suzi Jane Hokom, but it was his 1967 version with Nancy Sinatra that would prove more successful. In 1969 Lee Hazlewood performed the song on Swedish television with Swedish singer Siw Malmkvist on the Together programme, which was also shown at Montreux festival.', 'Lead Vocals‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄBass‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄDrums‚†Ä‚ÄĘ‚†ÄGuitar', NULL, '453', '22', '', '~Summer Wine~[{VV_not_found}]', NULL, NULL),
